{"id":443847928,"lang":"cpp","time":"11 months, 1 week","timestamp":1610839274,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"36 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/443847928/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"11.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        \n        int val = 0;\n        map<char,int> m1 = {{'I',1},{'V',5},{'X',10},{'L',50},{'C',100},{'D',500},{'M',1000}};\n        map<string,int> m2 = {{\"IV\",4},{\"IX\",9},{\"XL\",40},{\"XC\",90},{\"CD\",400},{\"CM\",900}};\n        \n        \n        int n = s.size();\n        for(int i = 0;i<n;i++){\n            bool f = 0;\n            if(i +1<n){\n                for(auto x : m2){\n                    if(s.substr(i,2) == x.first){\n                        val+= x.second;\n                        f = 1;\n                        i++;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n            if(f) continue;\n            for(auto x : m1){\n                if(s[i] == x.first) val += x.second;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return val;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer"}
